qacOutliers: Identification of Multivariate and Univariate Outliers

Source: R/qacOutliers-package.R
qacOutliers-package.Rd

The goal of qacOutliers is to detect multivariate and univariate outliers using seven different methods. This package consolidates methods from multiple different R packages and makes them more easily accessible.
